{"tid":153988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳志雲：TVB想直播曹星如拳賽　反向主辦方攞播映費","createTime":"2017-03-13T03:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T07:12:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84b6b089721c420a40b0d4752e3cb33ac93be744","tid":153988,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170313/large/1489374188_4b2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170313%2Flarge%2F1489374188_4b2b.jpg&h=38cf494c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曹星如前晚成功取得職業生涯第21連勝，在灣仔會展擊倒日本拳手向井寬史，有中國手機商當晚買下facebook直播版權，直播高峰時有近15萬人一同收看，片段至今已共有超過152萬人觀看。<br />\n<br />\n商業電台《在晴朗的一天出發》主持人陳志雲今早在節目中表示，曾與拳賽主辦機構的人士閒談，期間對方透露在曹星如去年爭取第19連勝時，曾與無綫商討播映權，但對方反過來要求主辦機構向無綫支付播出費用，最終合作告吹。<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲稱，受歡迎、有觀眾的內容，按照慣例，播映機構應向主辦機構付播映費，而非反過來。"},{"pid":"5850b3c4c2a75c53298ab2eea5f2317f8df17140","tid":153988,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲以為自己大台咩<br />\n慳啲囉"},{"pid":"14f4ae90734b9aab3269f70baf36fa18a38f7e95","tid":153988,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲以為自己大台咩<br />\n慳啲啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e951dacd8114745c93a1dbc7f4e85cd34fb3eaf","tid":153988,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲以為自己大台咩<br />\n慳啲啦</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e9249aa0ec5c627e5f63efca4629fdb